===============================================================
A podcast manager written for Android
===============================================================

This software is a podcatcher targeted for devices
running Google's Android. It features an intuitive three column 
layout and basic playback functionality. Multiple feeds are 
supported. Feeds can be searched while playing. The podcast 
description is displayed, supporting HTML content.

Visit http://www.podcatcher-deluxe.com for more information.

